{"arkId":"cl010278907","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010278907","modified ":"2026-01-17","title":"statue","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"statue (fragment, t\u00eate)"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : romain imp\u00e9rial\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 2e quart IIIe s. ap. J.-C. (225 - 250)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":true,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":225,"endYear":250,"imprecision":"","text":"2e quart IIIe s. ap. J.-C.","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"AGRR 3","type":"Autre num\u00e9ro d\u0027inventaire"},{"value":"Ma 5664","type":"Num\u00e9ro catalogue"},{"value":"Ma 4885","type":"Num\u00e9ro catalogue"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"femme (portrait, cheveux, en bandeau, torsad\u00e9)\r\n\r\nEtat de l\u0027oeuvre : Il manque l\u0027arri\u00e8re de la nuque et le nez","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"40","displayDimension":"40 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"26","displayDimension":"26 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"19,5","displayDimension":"19,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"24","displayDimension":"24 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : marbre\r\nTechnique : ronde-bosse (sculpture)","placeOfCreation":"Asie mineure","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Historique de la base \u0022R\u00e9cup\u00e9ration artistique (MNR Rose-Valland)\u0022 : \r\nLorsque cette oeuvre a \u00e9t\u00e9 pr\u00e9sent\u00e9e \u00e0 la premi\u00e8re Commission de choix des oeuvres de la r\u00e9cup\u00e9ration artistique, le 27 octobre 1949 (1), aucun renseignement susceptible d\u0027\u00e9clairer son histoire pendant la Seconde Guerre mondiale n\u0027\u00e9tait connu (pas de num\u00e9ro allemand, ni de \u00abCentral Collecting Point\u00bb, aucune mention du convoi de retour vers la France).\r\nLes archives de la commission de r\u00e9cup\u00e9ration artistique mentionnent \u00e0 plusieurs reprises \u0022une t\u00eate de femme antique\u0022. De ce fait, quelques hypoth\u00e8ses existent quant \u00e0 sa provenance. Mais aucun \u00e9l\u00e9ment pr\u00e9cis ne permet de reconna\u00eetre cet objet dans l\u0027une ou l\u0027autre de ces citations. L\u0027oeuvre est attribu\u00e9e aux mus\u00e9es nationaux (mus\u00e9e du Louvre, d\u00e9partement des antiquit\u00e9s grecques et romaines) en 1951 (2). Une d\u00e9charge sign\u00e9e par Georges Salles le 9 novembre 1949 atteste de son arriv\u00e9e au mus\u00e9e du Louvre (3).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"attribution par l\u0027office des biens et int\u00e9r\u00eats priv\u00e9s (MNR)","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Mus\u00e9es Nationaux R\u00e9cup\u00e9ration","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"attribution par l\u0027office des biens et int\u00e9r\u00eats priv\u00e9s (MNR)"}],"denomination":[{"value":"statue"},{"value":"fragment"},{"value":"t\u00eate"}],"material":[{"value":"marbre"}],"technic":[{"value":"ronde-bosse"}],"description":[{"value":"cheveux"},{"value":"portrait"},{"value":"femme"},{"value":"en bandeau"},{"value":"torsad\u00e9"}],"period":[{"value":"romain imp\u